{"id":159,"date":"2017-07-20T13:25:28","date_gmt":"2017-07-20T13:25:28","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hoodbuilder.dev\/?page_id=159"},"modified":"2023-11-19T05:24:18","modified_gmt":"2023-11-19T05:24:18","slug":"design","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/design\/","title":{"rendered":"Commercial Kitchen Design &#038; Remodeling"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\"><p>[vc_row css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1500556319702{background-color: #eeeeec !important;}&#8221;][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-2 vc_col-lg-8 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-10&#8243;]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e551c5f46c\" data-id=\"685e551c5f46c\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"big-para-blue\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hood Builder offers <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/construction\/\">standout restaurant construction<\/a>, kitchen design, and remodeling services with a quality guarantee. We serve the areas in Denver, Colorado and look forward to helping you develop your unique restaurant design.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; background-color: #0067ab;\">Free Quote 303-777-7720<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e551c5f485\" data-id=\"685e551c5f485\" data-height=\"60\" data-height-mobile=\"40\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"40\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column]<div class=\"ult-spacer spacer-685e551c5f494\" data-id=\"685e551c5f494\" data-height=\"90\" data-height-mobile=\"70\" data-height-tab=\"\" data-height-tab-portrait=\"\" data-height-mobile-landscape=\"70\" style=\"clear:both;display:block;\"><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-7 vc_col-md-7&#8243;][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you need restaurant exterior design or full-service interior design, our experts can help you create an eating environment your customers will love to visit.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><strong><span>Restaurant Kitchen Design<\/span> to Help You Stand Out in Your Industry<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our expert restaurant designers, engineers, and contractors possess the expertise and training to create renowned dining areas and commercial kitchen layouts while contributing to your profitability.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">For nearly thirty years, our restaurant construction team has been offering clients efficient kitchen spaces that look exceptional and yet perform practically all daily operations. Our restaurant interior designs are modern, efficient, and created to minimize your restaurant construction costs.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Here are just some of the services you can take advantage of when you hire Hood Builder for any sized construction project.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Restaurant space planning: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We help you get the most out of your available space by providing efficient and yet comfortable seating arrangements for your loyal customers.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Design &amp; Decor: <\/b>The overall look of a restaurant influences customer psychology. If you plan to make a good impression and draw in more customers, you should make sure the layout, architecture, colors, seating, light, and music are done right. We have a team of highly skilled interior designers who have mastered the art of building a wonderful customer experience through striking design. Whether you\u2019re looking for an ultra-modern look or a rustic ambiance, you can always rely on our professionals to deliver results that create mass appeal.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Color board design &amp; 3D renderings: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We have architects and interior designers who know how to plan a restaurant build-out from the ground up. Using the latest software, we can show you how your restaurant will look, with color and three-dimensional images, allowing you to approve the project before we begin.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Exterior design &amp; upgrades: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">Your curb appeal is your chance to make a great first impression with your customers. And don\u2019t forget your signage, which can bring loyal patrons from all around. We can make your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/general-contracting\/architectural-drawing\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">restaurant exterior design<\/span><\/a> stand out and get noticed for years to come.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Marketing displays, uniform design &amp; graphic design: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We don\u2019t just handle the construction and remodeling of your establishment. We can also help you come up with your logo, menu designs, and even design your staff \u2019s uniforms. We can handle it all. Just let our creative geniuses loose, and your marketing is assured to deliver customers from all over.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b><span>Give Your Commercial Kitchen an Eye-Catching Look through Innovative Layout and Design<\/span>: <\/b><\/h3>\n<p style=\"font-weight: 400; display: inline;\">We want to ensure your commercial kitchen staff has the room to move around and prepare meals to the best of their abilities. The ideal kitchen layout will make this happen and more. We can also ensure that your appliances are spaced appropriately to save on energy costs while adhering to all fire and safety codes.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"display: inline;\"><b>Fixtures, furnishings &amp; equipment:<\/b><\/h3>\n<p><span> Do you want a specific type of table or chair or kitchen appliance? If we can source it, we can procure it for you to complete your restaurant design in true style.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Schedule a Consultation\u00a0<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Call and tell us about your restaurant design needs. Once you have given us your concepts for the perfect design, we will begin the concept phase of your restaurant construction project. Your design will include a space-conserving kitchen and <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/restaurant-services\/remodeling\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">attractive dining room layout<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. We will also work with your interior designers, architects, and operations personnel to ensure your design flows nicely. We want you to be proud of the design we provide for you, and with Hood builder, your satisfaction is assured.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><b>Turnkey Restaurant Services<\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We keep a customer-first mindset. This means that we provide timely and accurate restaurant design services that keep to your schedule and budget. We also strive to provide top-notch customer service. When you call to speak to one of our <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/about-us\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">restaurant design-build specialists<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, you can rest assured that your concerns will be alleviated and all questions answered in a professional and timely manner. You will feel comfortable working with our experts, as we have your best interests in mind at all times.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In short, for complete restaurant installation and design services, along with all the materials you need to get your restaurant fully operational by opening day, you are encouraged to leave all the work to us.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>For a full and honest quote, <\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/contact-us\/\"><b>contact Hood Builder<\/b><\/a><b> today.<\/b><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"tel:+1-303-777-7720\" style=\"padding: 10px 20px 10px 20px; background-color: #0067ab;\">Free Quote 303-777-7720<\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][vc_column offset=&#8221;vc_col-lg-offset-1 vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-offset-1 vc_col-md-4&#8243;][vc_wp_custommenu nav_menu=&#8221;9&#8243; el_class=&#8221;wps-sidebar-related-links&#8221; title=&#8221;Related Links&#8221;]<div class=\"templatera_shortcode\"><div id=\"\" class=\"wps-row-container vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" ><div class=\"container wps-vc-container\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner \"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"\/services\/restaurant-services\/\" title=\"Restaurant Services\">\n\n            <div id=\"wps-sidebar-btn-410783\" class=\"sidebar-widget-button-details\">\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button-text\">\n                    <p>Restaurant Services<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"sidebar-widget-arrow\">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/wp-content\/themes\/wps-hoodbuilder\/assets\/images\/icon-arrow-sidebar-services.svg\" alt=\"\">\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div\n        class=\"sidebar-widget-button-wrap \">\n    <div class=\"sidebar-widget-button\">\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hoodbuilder.com\/services\/fire-suppression-systems\/\" titl